content.body:
### Shop 285/70R19.5 Tire Size 
The 285/70R19.5 tire size is designed for use on commercial vehicles such as light and medium-duty trucks, interstate buses, route pickup and delivery trucks, box trucks, service vans, and dump trucks. For these kinds of commercial applications, you’ll need a tire that’s tough enough for long hours on the road with low heat buildup, as well as retreadability, excellent load rating, and good traction on wet or dry pavement. 

Looking for a new set of 285/70R19.5 tires for your commercial vehicle? Check out the Goodyear Regional RHD II G131, [Continental ContiHybrid 3](https://simpletire.com/brands/continental-tires/conti-hybrid-hs3), Bridgestone R227F, and Roadmaster RM170 as each tire delivers excellent performance and value for fleet operators.

Whether you drive a medium-duty truck, interstate bus, box truck, or something else, SimpleTire has a set of 285/70R19.5 tires that meets your needs at a great price!
